                      icon: const Icon(Icons.undo),
                      label: const Text('Deshacer'),
                    ),
                  ),
                  const SizedBox(width: 6),
                  Expanded(
                    child: OutlinedButton.icon(
                      onPressed: clearGeofence,
                      icon: const Icon(Icons.delete),
